{{Infobox website | name = netd | logo = Netd logo 2013.png | company_type = | traded_as = | foundation = | dissolved = | location = | locations = | incorporated = | area_served = | founder = | chairman = | chairperson = | president = | CEO = | MD = | GM = | key_people = | industry = | products = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | assets = | equity = | owner = [[Doğan Media Group]] | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | url = {{URL|http://www.netd.com/}} | programming_language = | ipv6 = | alexa = Turkey 964<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/netd.com |title=Netd.com Traffic, Demographics and Competitors |website=Alexa.com |date= |accessdate=2017-05-23}}</ref> | website_type = [[Video on demand]] | advertising = | registration = Optional | num_users = | language = [[Turkish language|Turkish]] | launch_date = 11 January 2013 | current_status = Active | screenshot = | caption = | footnotes = | intl = }} {{lowercase title}}
'''''netd''''' is a [[video on demand]] web site launched in Turkey on 11 January 2013.<ref>{{cite web|title=Internetteki eğlence kanalınız "netd" artık yayında!|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/magazin/televizyon/22340182.asp|publisher=[[Hürriyet]]|accessdate=13 January 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=İnternetteki eğlence kanalınız "netd" yayında!|url=http://www.cnnturk.com/2013/bilim.teknoloji/%C4%B1nternet/01/11/internetteki.eglence.kanaliniz.netd.yayinda/692206.0/index.html|publisher=[[CNN Türk]]|accessdate=13 January 2013}}</ref> Netd is owned by [[Doğan Media Group]] and offers TV series mostly broadcast on [[Kanal D]], a Doğan Holding channel. As of January 2013,{{when|date=December 2013}} popular TV series like ''[[Kuzey Güney]]'', ''[[Yalan Dünya]]'', ''[[Leyla ile Mecnun]]'', ''Seksenler'', and ''[[Öyle Bir Geçer Zaman Ki]]'' can be watched online, as well as old popular TV series like ''[[Aşk-ı Memnu (TV series)|Aşk-ı Memnu]]'', ''[[Kavak Yelleri]]'' and ''[[Fatmagül'ün Suçu Ne?]]''. The web site also offers monthly free movies window, Kids Section, TV shows and 6 live broadcasts.
On 24 March 2014, NETD launched its music service with a motto of "Türkçe Müzikte İlk Durak - First Stop For Turkish Music".
All the content is free and ad-supported, there is no paid version. Videos are in up to 720p HD quality, live broadcasting and some content is in SD.
== Competitors == The web site launched about one month after [[Tvyo]], a similar service by [[Doğuş Media Group]].<ref>{{cite web|title='tvyo' yayına başladı!|url=http://www.cnbce.com/yasam-ve-teknoloji/internet/-tvyo--yayina-basladi|publisher=[[CNBC-e]]|accessdate=13 January 2013}}</ref> Previously, Apple [[iTunes Store]] opened for Turkey on 4 December 2012 only for music and films.<ref>{{cite web|title=Apple Launches iTunes Store in Russia, Turkey, India, South Africa & 52 Additional Countries Today|url=https://www.apple.com/pr/library/2012/12/04Apple-Launches-iTunes-Store-in-Russia-Turkey-India-South-Africa-52-Additional-Countries-Today.html|publisher=[[Apple Inc.]]|accessdate=13 January 2013}}</ref> [[TTNET]] also has a similar subscription-based service, [[Tivibu]].
== netd specials == netd offers netd.com only shows such as: * Kaybedenler Kulübü * Kronos - Mini Serials * Seksi Sorun * Ask Para Kariyer * Evden Uzakta - Music * Ömür Törpüsü * Sisenin Dibi * Sosyal Kafa * Dehsetin Taniklari * Sokak Röportajları * Yan Masa * Kafa Jello [[ReklamD]]
== netd live channels == NETD has 9 live channels. Kanal D, CNN Turk, Dream TV, Dream Turk, TV2, Tay TV, DShopping, NetD Live. NETD also started broadcasting [[Disney Channel Turkey]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.disneyturkiye.com.tr/disney-tv/disney-channel/ |title=Disney Channel - Türkiye Resmi Ana Sayfası |website=Disneyturkiye.com.tr |date= |accessdate=2017-05-23}}</ref> in mid of October 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnnturk.com/2013/guncel/10/11/disney.channel.eglenceli.icerigiyle.netdde/726924.0/index.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2013-10-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200302/http://www.cnnturk.com/2013/guncel/10/11/disney.channel.eglenceli.icerigiyle.netdde/726924.0/index.html |archivedate=2013-10-29 |df= }}</ref> NETD also broadcasts live programs during the day such as ''Sosyal Kafa'' (Social media review program), ''Ask Para Kariyer'' (Astrology and Angel Cards), and ''Kaybedenler Kulübü'' (Live Radio Program).
