{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}} The '''Robert Award for Best Actress in a Supporting Television Role''' ({{lang-da|Robert Prisen for årets kvindelige birolle – tv-serie}}) is one of the merit awards presented by the [[Danish Film Academy]] at the annual [[Robert Awards]] ceremony. The award has been handed out since 2013.
== Honorees == === 2010s === * 2013: [[Birthe Neumann]] – ''[[Julestjerner]]''<ref name="DRhiI" /> * 2014: [[Camilla Bendix]] – ''[[The Bridge (Danish/Swedish TV series)|Broen II]]''<ref name="jJyP8" /> * 2015: [[Lene Maria Christensen]] – ''[[The Legacy (TV series)|The Legacy]]''<ref name="wUWWh" /> {{Portal|Film|Denmark}} == References == {{reflist|refs= <ref name="DRhiI">{{cite web | url = http://www.juleweb.dk/nyhed032013.htm | title = Birthe Neumann vinder Robert for rolle i Julestjerner – Juleweb | publisher = | accessdate = 8 March 2015 }}</ref> <ref name="jJyP8">{{cite web | url = http://www.billedbladet.dk/kendte/danmark/tv/dr/camilla-bendix-fik-en-robert | title = Camilla Bendix fik en Robert | work = Billed Bladet | accessdate = 8 March 2015 }}</ref> <ref name="wUWWh">{{cite web | url = http://tvtid.tv2.dk/2015-02-01-se-listen-her-er-alle-robert-vinderne | title = Se listen: Her er alle Robert-vinderne | work = Tvtid.tv2.dk | accessdate = 8 March 2015 }}</ref> }}
